'''''Bad Kid, Good Gift''''' is an [[Adventure Mission]] in the chapter [[Amphoreus Annals]].

==Steps==
# Move a bit further from the children and think about the current situation
# Speak with the guard at Dawncloud
# Check the fallen guards
# (Optional) Investigate the ordinary guard lying on the ground
# (Optional) Investigate the Mountain Dweller lying on the ground
# Trace the lingering Fragment of Recollection near the fallen guards
# Figure out the next move
# Hide behind the Kephale statue and get ready for your act
# Sneak away from behind the statue
# Go to the frontline fighting against the black tide

